Class AltColorSpace

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class AltColorSpace
extends ColorSpace
    Color Space implementation for handling the PDF AlternateColorSpace. A PDF function is applied to colorvalues before converting. Author Katja Sondermann
